      "charEnd": 1555,
      "charStart": 1435,
      "factId": "hz.web.db8e6ed260cf41f3.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "To be a part of the webring, each site has a common navigation bar ; it contains links to the previous and next sites.",
      "tokens": [
